[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    365[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         enrollment_bucket: Bucket with the stored enrollment photo
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    366[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         enrollment_key: Key for the enrollment photo
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    367[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    368[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Returns:
